Thursday July 17, 2008.

Alex welcomes William Pepper, attorney representing the King family in the wrongful death lawsuit of Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr., and the Australian film producer Eva Orner, who produced the documentary Taxi to the Dark Side, winner of the 2008 Academy Award for Best Documentary and the Critics' Award at the Cannes Film Festival. In-studio guest today is the author of Mysterious Monuments, Texe Marrs. 

